{"tid":1363150,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A/PC] 龍珠 z bucchigiri match [1] 1周年入坑時機","createTime":"2019-07-25T05:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T18:55:58.000Z","uid":254214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec3f89cd2c512d5d2816d5a2c6e49a1b29c094b","tid":1363150,"uid":254214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/25/2ELIW4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F2ELIW4.png&h=0879e1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲形為實時1對1對戰卡牌遊戲<br />\n隻game特點係用html5整概網頁遊戲，完全唔使安裝，只要用個browser就玩到<br />\n絕對適合扮工室人士遊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲網址: <a href=\"https://dbz-bm.enza.fun/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdbz-bm.enza.fun%2F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=599d3d5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://dbz-bm.enza.fun/</a><br />\n<br />\n小小簡介：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=04198&amp;snA=28607&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=subbsn_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D04198%26snA%3D28607%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3Dsubbsn_8&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=a959d0d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=04198&amp;snA=28607&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=subbsn_8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.qoo-app.com/post/132045/%E3%80%90Qoo%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A+HTML5+%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%83%E9%BE%8D%E7%8F%A0Z+%E7%B5%95%E5%B0%8D%E5%8B%9D%E8%B2%A0%E3%80%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E9%80%99%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%AA%E6%AF%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B8%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%8C%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.qoo-app.com%2Fpost%2F132045%2F%25E3%258