"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa2ebb407d3c0a64c691f626752308105a1f8d36","tid":1363150,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34519903218c82f371f76e0497a954adf4eed59a","tid":1363150,"uid":43177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾GAME一隻<br />\n當你勝率高到某個位，佢就會NERF你抽牌<br />\n必輸<br />\n次次連贏一後時間天下大會(打電腦) 一星期左右<br />\n就會輸到仆街<br />\n電腦永遠抽到嘅牌係AR大過你1<br />\n去到後面佢就會多氣過你<br />\n每次比AR都只會係電腦贏<br />\n完全冇戰術可言<br />\nON撚99抽牌上輸比佢<br />\n垃撚圾GAME"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無諗過係人問題<br />\n唔識砌牌組 或睇人地咩牌<br />\n係on9 dd <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識砌牌唔識睇牌就唔會連勝啦<br />\n對戰都升到上Z rank  打神 rank 都有時贏到<br />\n講緊天下第一上級啲電腦boss呀懵撚<br />\n佢計撚住啲牌 抽返嚟嘅牌點都大撚過你呀<br />\n戰術冇用呀懵撚<br />\n唔係話次次都係咁<br />\n而係佢到某個時間點就set 好左會咁樣抽牌 等你天下pt 冇升得咁易<br />\n睇清楚先回啦懵撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁呢種叫輸唔起<br />\n贏就技術<br />\n輸就內定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40f437b84c41ce7d1bbe8828d8071ca3ed9b1ca","tid":1363150,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"btw 2017年就想無痛自殺<br />\n人生輸家 難怪打機都要怨天怨運氣"},{"pid":"07f5b40923cfa713d2885e4733cb8b928faaefa4","tid":1363150,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"世界上有一種人注定廢<br />\n就係你呢種<br />\n輸就賴運氣<br />\n贏就靠自己<br />\n生活不如意就賴命苦<br />\n要生要死<br />\n<br />\n可憐係你身邊受你負能量既人<br />\n遠離好友 咪害人啦"},{"pid":"25bcdb213dec32547410824d9a5f0f3c54d9c3eb","tid":1363150,"uid":28962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"人地都係屌隻game姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你就人身攻擊"}]}